OL,3,CMan, 76, to appear in court over
OL,4,Csummer camp 'poisoning'
OL,6,FA 76-year-old man will appear in court
OL,7,Fcharged with child cruelty offences
OL,8,Fafter children became unwell at a
OL,9,Fsummer camp in Leicestershire.
OL,11,FLeicestershire Police said it received
OL,12,Fa report on Sunday that children at a
OL,13,Fsummer camp at Stathern Lodge in Canal
OL,14,FLane, Stathern, had become unwell.
OL,16,FEight children, all boys aged between
OL,17,Feight and 11, and an adult, who were
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital as a precaution,
OL,19,Fhave all since been discharged.
