OL,3,CMan, 76, to appear in court over
OL,4,Csummer camp 'poisoning'
OL,6,FJonathon Ruben, of Landmere Lane,
OL,7,FRuddington, Nottingham, has been
OL,8,Fcharged with three counts of wilful
OL,9,Fill treatment relating to three boys
OL,10,Fat the summer camp between July 25 and
OL,11,FJuly 29, the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,12,Fsaid on Friday.
OL,14,FHe was remanded into custody and will
OL,15,Fappear at Leicester Magistrates' Court
OL,16,Fon Saturday.
