OL,3,CMan, 76, to appear in court over
OL,4,Csummer camp 'poisoning'
OL,6,FRuben, 76, was originally arrested on
OL,7,FMonday evening at a pub on suspicion
OL,8,Fof administering poison or a noxious
OL,9,Fthing with intent to injure, aggrieve
OL,10,For annoy.
OL,12,FSentencing Council guidelines state
OL,13,Fthat ill treatment of a child can
OL,14,Fresult in a maximum sentence of 14
OL,15,Fyears' imprisonment under the Children
OL,16,Fand Young Persons Act 1933.
OL,18,FLeicestershire Police has referred
OL,19,Fitself to the Independent Office for
OL,20,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) over its
OL,21,Fhandling of the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
