OL,3,CMan, 76, to appear in court over
OL,4,Csummer camp 'poisoning'
OL,6,FThe force originally said the incident
OL,7,Fhappened on Monday, before amending it
OL,8,Fto Sunday, and it is still unclear
OL,9,Fwhether officers only responded on
OL,10,FMonday, and whether that is why the
OL,11,Fforce has referred itself to the IOPC.
OL,13,FJanine McKinney, chief crown
OL,14,Fprosecutor for CPS East Midlands,
OL,15,Fsaid: "The Crown Prosecution Service
OL,16,Fhas authorised the prosecution of a 76-
OL,17,Fyear-old man with child cruelty
OL,18,Foffences following a police
OL,19,Finvestigation into a summer camp held
OL,20,Fat Stathern Lodge, Leicestershire.
