OL,3,CMan, 76, to appear in court over
OL,4,Csummer camp 'poisoning'
OL,6,F"This decision has been made after
OL,7,Freviewing a file of evidence from
OL,8,FLeicestershire Police.
OL,10,F"Jonathon Ruben will be charged with
OL,11,Fthree offences of wilful ill treatment
OL,12,Fof a child relating to three boys.
OL,14,F"This has been an extremely upsetting
OL,15,Fand shocking moment for the community,
OL,16,Fand especially for the children and
OL,17,Fparents most directly affected.
