OL,3,CMan, 76, to appear in court over
OL,4,Csummer camp 'poisoning'
OL,6,F"We would like to remind all concerned
OL,7,Fthat there are now active criminal
OL,8,Fproceedings against Mr Ruben, and he
OL,9,Fhas the right to a fair trial.
OL,11,F"There must be no reporting,
OL,12,Fcommentary or sharing of information
OL,13,Fonline that may in any way prejudice
OL,14,Fthese proceedings."
OL,16,FLeicestershire Police said the "owners
OL,17,Fand operators of Stathern Lodge are
OL,18,Findependent from those people who use
OL,19,For hire the lodge and are not
OL,20,Fconnected to the incident".
